This plugin adds the Google Translate Toolbar to your wordpress website/blog

== Description ==

To give multilanguage support for your website you can use this plugin. No code or content changes is required.
Just install this translator widget

== Installation ==

1. Upload `google_translate_toolbar.php` to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory
1. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
1. Place `<?php do_action('plugin_name_hook'); ?>` in your templates

== Frequently Asked Questions ==

= Do I need to prepare contents in multiple languages? =

No, Just install this plugin. Google translation will take care about it. 

